name: FNF: Deep-Sea Date - Suvarna (test)
description:
DISCLAIMER: this test was built using Neko due to issues with compiling to Windows.

The FNF character test that was lost for █████████ years has finally been uncovered for all to play! Mess about with Suvarna's animations, much like all previous FNF character tests!

Controls

Up, Down, Left and Right = *elegant crystal sounds*

W, A, S and D = *creepypasta intensifies*
